398
00:26:29,715 --> 00:26:30,555
Yan He.

399
00:26:30,955 --> 00:26:31,795
So eager

400
00:26:32,154 --> 00:26:33,394
to poach him?

401
00:26:34,114 --> 00:26:35,914
Shouldn't you ask me first?

402
00:26:36,715 --> 00:26:37,555
Cold Xiao,

403
00:26:37,874 --> 00:26:38,834
