478
00:31:02,594 --> 00:31:03,434
Commander Xiao.

479
00:31:08,755 --> 00:31:09,595
It's been a while,

480
00:31:11,515 --> 00:31:12,355
General He.

481
00:31:26,114 --> 00:31:27,475
